	Other eBay rulesets:

		- ebay.at.xml
		- ebay.be.xml
		- ebay.ca.xml
		- ebay.ch.xml
		- ebay.co.uk.xml
		- ebay.com.au.xml
		- ebay.com.hk.xml
		- ebay.com.my.xml
		- ebay.com.sg.xml
		- ebay.de.xml
		- ebay.es.xml
